snippet.title: Planetary Life - Trailer (Remake)
snippet.description:
Planetary Life is a planet, life and evolution simulation game.

#evolution #simulator #nature

🎮 Wishlist now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2471970/Planetary_Life?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=trailer2

🌍 Discord server:
https://discord.gg/rN4KFgkVu8

🔥 Follow on Twitter:
https://twitter.com/pitxardo
https://twitter.com/sotenbox

Modify the climate and shape the planet. 
Create some life and evolve it until they create the first civilizations.
Planets and creatures are procedurally generated.
